Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.65,0:22:29.53,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(152,152)\blur1}想要被射穿的心 要在她之前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.07,0:22:34.04,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(152,152)\blur1}人為什麼 為什麼會是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.08,0:22:37.83,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(152,152)\blur1}無論受傷多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.92,0:22:44.21,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(152,152)\blur1}都會墜入愛河的生物
